('General Education','Mathematics','medium','The area of a triangle with base 10 cm and height 6 cm is:','[{"key": "A", "text": "30 cm\u00b2"}, {"key": "B", "text": "60 cm\u00b2"}, {"key": "C", "text": "16 cm\u00b2"}, {"key": "D", "text": "80 cm\u00b2"}]','A','The correct answer is A. 30 cm².','elementary'),
