('General Education','Science','medium','Which type of cloud is associated with heavy rain?','[{"key": "A", "text": "Cirrus"}, {"key": "B", "text": "Cumulus"}, {"key": "C", "text": "Cumulonimbus"}, {"key": "D", "text": "Stratus"}]','C','The correct answer is C. Cumulonimbus.','elementary'),
('General Education','Science','medium','Which gas do plants absorb from the atmosphere during photosynthesis?','[{"key": "A", "text": "Oxygen"}, {"key": "B", "text": "Nitrogen"}, {"key": "C", "text": "Carbon Dioxide"}, {"key": "D", "text": "Hydrogen"}]','C','The correct answer is C. Carbon Dioxide.','elementary'),
