('Professional Education','Principles of Teaching','hard','Realia as an instructional material refers to:','[{"key": "A", "text": "Digital presentations"}, {"key": "B", "text": "Actual real-life objects used in teaching"}, {"key": "C", "text": "Printed textbooks"}, {"key": "D", "text": "Flashcards"}]','B','The correct answer is B. Actual real-life objects used in teaching.','elementary'),
('Professional Education','Principles of Teaching','hard','The teacher''s role in cooperative learning is to be a:','[{"key": "A", "text": "Controller of all activity"}, {"key": "B", "text": "Facilitator and guide"}, {"key": "C", "text": "Sole source of information"}, {"key": "D", "text": "Evaluator only"}]','B','The correct answer is B. Facilitator and guide.','elementary'),
('Professional Education','The Teaching Profession','hard','A teacher''s primary loyalty should be to:','[{"key": "A", "text": "The principal"}, {"key": "B", "text": "The Department of Education"}, {"key": "C", "text": "The learners and their development"}, {"key": "D", "text": "The community"}]','C','The correct answer is C. The learners and their development.','elementary'),
