('Professional Education','The Teaching Profession','hard','The Magna Carta for Teachers (RA 4670) guarantees teachers'':','[{"key": "A", "text": "Right to own school property"}, {"key": "B", "text": "Security of tenure, salary, and professional rights"}, {"key": "C", "text": "Right to refuse school assignments"}, {"key": "D", "text": "Right to grade students subjectively"}]','B','The correct answer is B. Security of tenure, salary, and professional rights.','elementary'),
