('General Education','Social Studies','medium','The Filipino value of ''hiya'' refers to:','[{"key": "A", "text": "Pride in achievement"}, {"key": "B", "text": "Sensitivity to social acceptance and avoiding embarrassment"}, {"key": "C", "text": "Respect for elders"}, {"key": "D", "text": "Love for country"}]','B','The correct answer is B. Sensitivity to social acceptance and avoiding embarrassment.','elementary'),
